<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw, Lalpa, naupangte'n ka hun chiel ui,
 Na mel deihum leh Na pau kamsuok thum tak
 Het ka nuom muh ka nuom ui.

[V2]
 Aw, nang ka Lal leh ka Tanpau, ka Puipau Na hi,
 Ka kikhawpnau leh thilpiek,
 Nang di'n lopina hi hen, kei u din vangsakna
 Van chana kipahna di'n.

[V3]
 2. Malai khan naupan neuhaw Na lawpa,
 &quot;Ka kawmah hun pui un, gai, kiu in&quot; Na tii,
 Naupang kipahna a kim.

[V4]
 3. Puipa di'n Thagau Thiengtho, hung lengin,
 Naupang neucha cha kikhawmhaw ma hung puiin,
 Lal nasep khawk dan hilh in.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Lal Leh Tanpau</title>
<hymn_number>300</hymn_number>
<author>Pautinkhup</author>
</song>